{"tid":154682,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［電腦白痴］螢幕無訊號","createTime":"2017-03-13T12:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T18:33:02.000Z","uid":13583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"200bfb381972881be5e4791a74a7933ed3e4a2e9","tid":154682,"uid":13583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"如題，小弟我今朝個螢幕都好地地，不過個cpu過熱，熄咗機，所以就拆咗個風扇掃麈。裝番好之後個螢幕就話d-sub無訊號，但我好很肯定個主機係開緊，因為風扇有轉+有著燈。<br />\n我已經試過重裝顯卡/ram，換埋條線，但都冇用，請問仲可以點搞？<br />\n個螢幕係 LG 19EN33<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLtK7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLtK7X.jpg&h=08fde486&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5e935fbdcc7eb1c17fbd7ce11ab33fb5cf12ece","tid":154682,"uid":34411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6295169bfe02a9f09f112db06d8e255e0ad55adc","tid":154682,"uid":13583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"拆咗都係冇訊號，點條ram有冇問題"},{"pid":"5580dba576d91765c1d9a72be5c69f462da21a3c","tid":154682,"uid":13583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"拆咗都係冇訊號，點睇條ram有冇問題"},{"pid":"503ac24f81adf7640e30783b0f3e6244605c6fb2","tid":154682,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拆咗都係冇訊號，點睇條ram有冇問題</blockquote><br />\n如果有2條ram就試下拆其中一條 之後開機 <br />\n同樣方法試埋 第二條 睇下個MON有冇野睇/部機開唔開到<br />\n利申: 識少少 好似係"},{"pid":"f2af5783bb028f4e7b9f6ebe0dd929c49cf10102","tid":154682,"uid":34411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e6d9f25ef76571761051c7f320e4c99840d5b93","tid":154682,"uid":13583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T15:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拆咗都係冇訊號，點條ram有冇問題</blockquote><br />\n開機有冇嘟嘟聲?<br />\n有多條既, 就放另一條入唔同ram位試下<br />\n可果冇嘟嘟聲都係開唔到就好大機會嬈左底板<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘟嘟聲即係點，我開機係&quot;咚嘟咇⋯＂咁嘅聲（咁上下啦 <br />\n另外兩條ram點放都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0cdc5fb989cbc36b6af78a7810a596584e462e","tid":154682,"uid":214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:33:02.000Z","msg":"我部電腦如果開機既時候load緊野會無啦啦熄左機（因為潮濕關係）再開既時候就會無畫面，咁我就會開喇叭，聽聲等佢入到window 再用keyboard 熄機（window&gt;右箭咀&gt;enter)聽到佢正常熄機，再開個mon就會有返野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次都work你可以試下"}]}